## Dataset media and captions (public domain)

Unless a specific file says otherwise, the image files under `media/` and their
matching `.txt` caption sidecars are dedicated to the **public domain**.

To the extent possible under law, the author has waived all copyright and
related or neighboring rights to those media and caption files worldwide.
You may copy, modify, distribute, and use them — including for commercial
purposes and for training machine-learning models — without asking permission.

If a jurisdiction does not recognize public-domain dedications, the media and
captions are licensed under [CC0 1.0 Universal](https://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/).

Third-party trademarks, logos, or identifiable people appearing *inside*
photographs are not transferred by this license; only the author's copyright
interest in the files is waived.
